knowledge_graph.merchant_description: "Student Union, Inc. Spartan Recreation and Aquatic Center was awarded the Athletic Business Facility of the year award and NIRSA Facility of Merit in 2021. We are available for SJSU matriculated students, faculty, and staff to participate in our state of the art facilities. We are here to help you continue or start a healthy and active lifestyle with various programs. Join a fitness class, take a climb on our 40' climbing or bouldering walls, take a swim in one of our (3) pools, or join an intramural or club sport team. Not sure where to start on your fitness journey, our personal training program to get you started on your goals. We look forward to seeing you soon."
